{"tid":2124671,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[7月新番] 《戀與製作人》","createTime":"2020-07-25T14:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T12:11:36.000Z","uid":34609,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6577b7113987e62ec22a2a33e612d964789f9b34","tid":2124671,"uid":34609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AKcYraK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAKcYraK.jpg&h=4220cff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇情簡介<br />\n《戀與製作人》的世界觀圍繞著特殊能力「EVOL」。作為製作人的女主角繼承了父親所留下的影視公司，在挽救瀕臨破產的公司並試圖打造最優質節目的過程中，將偶然認識擁有不同 EVOL 的 4 位男主角&mdash;李澤言、周棋洛、白起及許墨，同時一步步深陷 EVOL 的特殊能力謎團，就此和男主角們展開不可思議的旅程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原作：恋とプロデューサー～ EVOL &times; LOVE Papergames<br />\n監督：境宗久<br />\n系列構成：𠮷村清子<br />\n角色設計：山口仁七<br />\n製作：崴智娯楽 Emoto Entertainment / CAAnimation<br />\n動畫製作：MAPPA<br />\n▍CAST<br />\n女主: 金元寿子<br />\n李澤言：杉田智和<br />\n周棋洛：柿原徹也<br />\n白起：小野友樹<br />\n許墨：平川大輔"},{"pid":"7e70116083079f442b631f32acb291e5054cc1f6","tid":2124671,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"呢部都可以動畫化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960bedbdca091ed73bb3df3e9bf9ca1cc88ff369","tid":2124671,"uid":34609,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人睇...<br />\n但個女主幾好J..........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠長腿..又玩OL套裝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CqFWcTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqFWcTK.jpg&h=e04668f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOACGM5.jpg\" data-thumbnail